* get rid of everything which is makeShared() related

* change everything from `PointCloud<Type>` to `PointCloud<Type>::Ptr` or `PointCloud<Type>::ConstPtr`

* cloud_segmentation_by_voting.cpp
  No clustering stage. Fit models to point cloud, multiple times, and build the parameter space.

* segmentation_by_voting.cpp
  Clustering stage. Fit models to each cluster, multiple times, and build a parameter space for every one of them.

